➜OLPC展示XO 3.0平板
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=27857	20700
每个孩子一台笔记本（OLPC）项目在CES上展示了<a href="http://arstechnica.com/gadgets/news/2012/01/charging-by-crank-bicycle-waterwheel-hands-on-with-the-olpc-xo-30-tablet.ars">售价100美元的XO 3.0平板</a>（不零售）。<i>
